# oracle harness: libharness.so is cross-compiled per-build (CI builds
# it in .github/workflows/differential.yml; local devs rebuild via the
# one-liner at tests/differential/oracle_runner/harness/CMakeLists.txt).
# Do not commit .so binaries — they bloat the repo history and rebuilds
# are fast (~10s with NDK clang).
tests/differential/oracle_runner/harness/prebuilt/libharness.so
